      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>In response to a petition from <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>, an official orders the revenue officer (karori) to stop displacing the people of <placeName ref="#sultanpur">Sultanpur</placeName> and instead
            settle the people and improve agriculture.</p>
         </abstract>
